OL,5, Dozens of allegations of safeguarding  
OL,6, failures in after-school clubs -       
OL,7, including assaults, neglect and sexual 
OL,8, abuse - have been uncovered by BBC     
OL,9, News.                                  
OL,11,FMore than 80 referrals have been made  
OL,12,Fabout clubs in school grounds in the   
OL,13,Fpast five years, according to          
OL,14,Finformation requests.                  
OL,16,FIn one incident, an eight-year-old boy 
OL,17,Fhad to clean his younger sister after  
OL,18,Fshe soiled herself. The Department for 
OL,19,FEducation says every child should feel 
OL,20,Fsafe in after-school clubs.            
